{"arkId":"cl010114980","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010114980","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Terrine \u00e0 fond d\u0027or et d\u00e9cor de fleurs bleu et or","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Terrine \u00e0 fond d\u0027or et d\u00e9cor de fleurs bleu et or"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1735","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1735,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"2e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Manufacture de Meissen","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q76941091"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 9592","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"terrine","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Terrine de forme cylindrique, \u00e0 couvercle bomb\u00e9 et aplati au sommet. La panse et le dessus enti\u00e8rement dor\u00e9, laissent voir le fond peint en cama\u00efeu bleu, d\u0027un d\u00e9cor (chinois ?) de fleurs et d\u0027arbrisseaux. Deux anses recourb\u00e9es en forme de poisson bleu \u00e0 \u00e9cailles noires et or, sont dispos\u00e9es obliquement sur la panse, l\u0027une et l\u0027autre en sens inverse. Une troisi\u00e8me anse, pareille aux premi\u00e8res, se dresse verticalement sur le couvercle. Bords moulur\u00e9s et dor\u00e9s. Revers non \u00e9maill\u00e9.","inscriptions":"Marque de l\u0027atelier : \r ; Deux \u00e9p\u00e9es entrecrois\u00e9es  (peinte en bleue sous gla\u00e7ure \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du pot)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"23,3","display